---
import Link from "@/components/ui/link.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      Unabhängig. Aktuell. Schweizerisch.
    </h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg text-blue-600 mt-1">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p>
          ki-anbieter.ch wurde geschaffen, um Orientierung zu bieten.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-green-50 rounded-lg text-green-600 mt-1">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p>
          Die Plattform ist unabhängig, redaktionell gepflegt und offen für neue Anbieter.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg text-purple-600 mt-1">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p>
          Du willst dein Unternehmen eintragen lassen oder hast eine Korrektur? Wir freuen uns auf deine Nachricht.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <Link href="/kontakt" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 group">
      Kontakt aufnehmen
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
      </svg>
    </Link>
  </div>
</section> 